headline: Trump's $13 Billion Mistake: President Could Have Bought Dallas Cowboys For $50 Million
summary: President Donald Trump's wealth has increased in recent years, with a big gain thanks to his stake in Trump Media & Technology Group (NASDAQ:DJT) and his family's cryptocurrency ventures. Things may have been different if Trump acquired an NFL team in 1980 with his wealth likely worth significantly more and his political ambitions possibly non-existent. headline: As Amazon Copies the Netflix Playbook, Can AMZN Stock Copy the 425% Gains in NFLX?
summary: Amazon is phasing out its Prime free shipping sharing, taking the lead from streaming companies that have cracked down on password sharing. While the move is an incremental positive, it does not materially alter the investment case for AMZN stock.
